            <li><strong>Keyboard Navigation:</strong> Full keyboard support with arrow keys, Enter, Escape, Tab, and Page Up/Down for calendar navigation</li>
            <li><strong>Screen Reader Support:</strong> Proper ARIA labels, live regions, and announcements for date selections and navigation</li>
            <li>
                <strong>ARIA Attributes:</strong> Uses <code>aria-label</code>, <code>aria-describedby</code>, <code>aria-live</code>, and <code>role</code> attributes
                for enhanced accessibility
            </li>
            <li><strong>Focus Management:</strong> Proper focus handling and visual focus indicators throughout the component</li>
            <li><strong>Date Announcements:</strong> Configurable announcements for selected dates and navigation changes</li>
            <li><strong>High Contrast Support:</strong> Respects system high contrast settings and provides clear visual distinctions</li>
            <li><strong>Form Integration:</strong> Works seamlessly with form labels, validation, and error messaging</li>
            <li><strong>Localization:</strong> Supports localized date formats and calendar navigation for international users</li>
        </ul>
